This webhook only fires if the order status has changed, such as `Pending` to `Awaiting Payment`

### Example callback:

```json
{
  "created_at": 1561482670,
  "store_id": "1025646",
  "producer": "stores/{store_hash}",
  "scope": "store/order/statusUpdated",
  "hash": "352e4afc6dd3fc85ea26bfdf3f91852604d57528",
  "data": {
    "type": "order",
    "id": 250,
    "status": {
      "previous_status_id": 1,
      "new_status_id": 11
    }
  }
}
```

